{"id": 1814, "genre": 1000, "title": "在日常生活中，你是哪一类型的手机摄影师？", "description": "你更多地把摄像头用来当做记录工具、社交工具、创作工具，还是玩具？(题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 10163, "comment_count": 34, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170724093923J1ZOdBITEl6gyFAt.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-31T17:00:16Z", "questions": [{"id": 2673, "title": "在日常生活中，你是哪一类型的手机摄影师？", "content": "日常中，你是哪一类型的手机摄影师？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 224465, "content": "“拍一张照片”型，主要常用手机自带照相APP", "image": "img/option/option/20170724094219rFqShxgZ3e2DN45Q.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 224467, "content": "“截屏型”，不太拍照，主要用来截屏或拍照给别人，说明些问题啥的", "image": "img/option/option/20170724095547MSZ06DwPJeN7mR3c.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 224477, "content": "“偶发性艺术创作”型，随时咔一下，不会花心思处理", "image": "img/option/option/20170724101430UGdua4MO973PXHNI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 224478, "content": "“景点型”，平时不太拍，手机里大部分照片都是出去旅行出差之类的时候拍的", "image": "img/option/option/20170724100240LEOfrKkdFxXZTS5V.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 224479, "content": "“生活如实记录型“，拍菜，拍路边猫狗，拍北京天气", "image": "img/option/option/20170724100356od9YDgzaSJmPBW1b.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 224483, "content": "“摄影APP研究型”，会使各种修图改图配表情工具，少有不处理就发出来的照片", "image": "img/option/option/20170724100719PyrJ6ocs1MKbpOjB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 224484, "content": "“摄影大师精进型”，构图光线取景一个都不能马虎", "image": "img/option/option/20170724100830pkFq7flQaMG6zNK5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 224486, "content": "“不拍型”，完全没有拍照的习惯和兴趣，手机里都没照片", "image": "img/option/option/20170724101025WQTxapij72oEcrLd.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}